This was the first occasion which I met Sean. Morg's had mentioned 
previously that he was leaving ASM and that Mr. Holland was taking over. 
There was a contest/demo at Taren Point and he'd be there. I was to 
introduce myself and take some snap's. Morg's mentioned that Sean is a skater, 
so rest assured I'd be in good hands with him becoming editor. Little did I 
know that he could skate so well. I don't think I even skated but shot tonnes 
of photos. I noticed Sean skating the mini. I moved my flashes over and quickly 
shot this Noseblunt slide. Nothing better than knowing your editor can skate 
better than you. 

Thank you Mr. Holland for all the opportunities which you gave myself. 
#thankyouskateboarding 

## @theskateboardersjournal 00'
## FSNBS
## Taren Point Vert X
